//  test_mamba2_ssd.hexa — Mamba-2 Structured State Space Duality tests
//
//  ML roadmap #193 — verifies self/ml/mamba2_ssd.hexa
//
//  Tests (40):
//    T1  ssd_abs positive
//    T2  ssd_abs negative
